-Yeah.

524
00:25:41.482 --> 00:25:44.159
Well. I've been on. like. one
million walking tours. truly.

525
00:25:44.193 --> 00:25:47.413
and you are very good
at what you do.

526
00:25:47.446 --> 00:25:48.747
Wow. really?

527
00:25:48.781 --> 00:25:50.624
