665
00:33:13.266 --> 00:33:14.943
I'm not shit at taking...

666
00:33:14.976 --> 00:33:16.953
-Oh. Damn it.
-Mm.

667
00:33:24.236 --> 00:33:25.328
You're a good man.

668
00:33:27.572 --> 00:33:29.040
I mean. I always knew you were.

669
00:33:29.074 --> 00:33:31.501
